    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine. This naturally aspirated mill utilizes VarioCam Plus for optimized valve lift and timing, delivering a linear power band and 320hp. The drivetrain is anchored by a G96 6-speed manual transaxle, providing precise shift throws and excellent mechanical feedback. The chassis retains its composure with an independent multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts, while braking performance remains sharp via four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled ventilated rotors. This example is in good condition, showing honest cosmetic wear consistent with its age, but remains robust where it counts\u2014the engine pulls strongly to redline and the synchros are smooth. A technically honest 911 for the discerning enthusiast.",
