      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a pampered showpiece and a reliable daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor stone chips and light surface marks expected of a car that has enjoyed the open road. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium leather seats remain supple with only slight softening on the driver's side bolster, and every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been meticulously serviced according to the manufacturer's schedule, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that starts eagerly every time. We recently completed a full fluid flush and comprehensive inspection to ensure it\u2019s turn-key ready for its next owner. If you are looking for a well-cared-for example that looks sharp and drives even better, this is an excellent opportunity.",
